Dances Up EarthquakesSPECIAL RULESBEGIN A DANCE OF DECADESWhenever you would play a Power Card, you may instead pay any amount of Energy onto the card to make it an impending card ({custom1}), setting it aside out of play for use on a future turn. (It doesn't provide Elements. It's still your Power Card, so it can be forgotten while it's impending.)RHYTHMIC POWER BUILDS TO A CATACLYSMIC CRESCENDOWhen you gain Energy from your Presence Track, also gain {custom5} Energy onto each Power Card made {custom1} on a previous turn. If any {custom1} now have Energy on them at least equal to their cost, discard that Energy and play them. (This costs no card plays.)If you have at least 1 {custom1}, Add 1 {custom6} in one of your lands.In one of your lands, Defend 1 per {custom1} (max. 3).If you have at least 3 {custom1}, Add 1 {custom6} in one of your lands.In one of your lands, Defend 1 per {custom1} (max. 3).2 Damage per {custom6}, to {town}/{city} only.1 {fear}. In any number of lands with {custom6}: 2 Damage per {custom6}, to {town}/{city} only. Remove 1 {custom6}.2 {fear}. In each land where you removed {custom6}: 1 Damage to each Invader.
